text: "Pregnant Again" is a 1980 song by Loretta Lynn and was released as a single via MCA Records. It was later included on her studio album Loretta and went to number 30 on the Billboard Hot Country Singles chart and number 13 on the Canadian Country Songs charts. == Track listings == ;7" vinyl single * "Pregnant Again" â€“ 3:35 * "You're a Cross I Can't Bear" ==References== Category:1980 songs Category:Country songs Category:Loretta Lynn songs
